[SN]TITLE[SN]
Danish school says no to having just one best friend

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Do you have someone that you consider to be your best friend? If you ask that question in one school in Denmark then the answer would definitely be no.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
